# Public Lynx — public docs AI chat

> **Status: active.** `app/api/chat/route.ts` + `#components2/ai/search` on `/{locale}/ask-docs`. Vercel AI SDK + AI Gateway (`@ai-sdk/gateway` via `#lib/ai/gateway.server`); no org session; no `#features/lynx` import.

---

## What it is

An AI chat dialog embedded in the public docs surface (`/{locale}/ask-docs`), branded as **Lynx**.

- Visitors ask questions about Afenda's product.
- The AI answers using ask-docs content (`llms-full.txt`, Orama index, or per-page `.md` endpoints).
- No org session required — fully public.

---

## What it is NOT

**It is not `lib/features/lynx/`** — that module is the authenticated, tenant-scoped ERP machine layer.

| | ERP Lynx (`lib/features/lynx/`) | Public Lynx (`app/api/chat/`) |
|---|---|---|
| Auth | `requireOrgSession()` — mandatory | None — public |
| Scope | One org's ERP data | Public docs content |
| Audit | `erp.lynx.*` events required | No ERP audit subject |
| Route | `app/api/erp/lynx/*` | `app/api/chat/route.ts` |
| Import | `#features/lynx` | Vercel AI SDK + AI Gateway |

**Never route the public chat through `lib/features/lynx/`.**
Doing so would either create a silent IDOR hole (no org session) or corrupt the Lynx audit contract.

---

## Prevented regressions (enforced in CI)

| Failure mode | Prevention |
|---|---|
| Public chat imports ERP Lynx | ESLint `afenda/public-lynx-boundary` + `pnpm lint:public-lynx-contract` |
| IAM session / audit on `/api/chat` | `scripts/check-public-lynx-contract.mjs` |
| `req.json()` bypasses body size cap | Route must use `readPublicLynxChatRequestBody` from `lib/ask-docs/public-lynx-request.shared.ts` |
| Duplicate transcript helpers in UI | `search.tsx` must use `buildPublicLynxConversationTranscript` + `extractPublicLynxMessageText` |
| Bare `pnpm exec vitest run` (no config) | `check-public-lynx-contract.mjs` requires `--config .config/vitest.config.ts` on every `package.json` vitest script |

**After touching this stack:** `pnpm lint:public-lynx-contract` and `pnpm exec vitest run --config .config/vitest.config.ts tests/unit/ask-docs/`.

**Unit tests:** always `pnpm test:fast` or `pnpm exec vitest run --config .config/vitest.config.ts` — never bare `vitest run` (skips `server-only` / `next/navigation` stubs → false failures).

---

## Branding contract

- Label in UI: **"Ask Lynx"** or **"Lynx"** — consistent with the authenticated ERP surface.
- Do NOT use: "AI assistant", "chatbot", "copilot", "AI mode". See `lynx-knowledge.mdc` banned vocabulary.
- Icon: use brand PNGs in `public/icons/lynx/` (`Lynx-transfrom-1.png` rest, `Lynx-transfrom-2.png` hover/open in light, `Lynx-transfrom-3.png` dark) via `LynxBrandMark` / `#lib/ask-docs/lynx-brand.shared` — full-fill round trigger, no padding. Never use lucide `MessageCircle` or generic robot/spark icons.

